signatures.text: inline fun CharSequence.minOfOrNull( selector: (Char) -> Double): Double?
signatures.desc: Returns the smallest value among all values produced by selector function applied to each character in the char sequence or null if there are no characters.

signatures.text: inline fun <R : Comparable<R>> CharSequence.minOfOrNull( selector: (Char) -> R): R?
signatures.desc: Returns the smallest value among all values produced by selector function applied to each character in the char sequence or null if there are no characters.
